/LZnBdRyY3w6Xm79-UlRxqHDGN8oPWCbf/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: inherit;" target="_blank" title="来自受损项目的大部分碳信用额被视为伪造"&gt;你将损失分配&lt;/a&gt;给大气。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;丹尼·卡伦沃德&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; margin: 0;"&gt;宾夕法尼亚大学气候经济学家&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;本周零&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 20px 0; background-color: #f0f0f0;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8G-gQaz5pgo4U9r_B5JPxw-b-cXgzw8uxGmZ2ybAUA59oNtI_Eh66AvCuCm9h8cHyGSwNfms8_u3h2SufShyrn6vZFVzMnr2az4eOHgYJZSmLcXwXAy5FGne474wcD5FGbEOW1SylqEBtN0ubjCTPw8uPbT5LHn1Qj47ZnZGDp0cU9VVUUpCMqqzcB0a97H3ZGgd6BYouEcUt9LNKq0mMQuZW1KSX2PdzECp3GD63cVJQgXlp5hg9McTsF6vUri6rp-qL0U6Mbz0yuUFDXhn0r_ErAKFOYzrfLeUp5BuRadz8PWzLkVvesYAbl6j_ntFYjrN-m7UvrZHt5IoOk1PyNy3pHU5GBH84uX1TrcDtuRvz0Tulpz1a6qBRXriq7mE0Xj02unG/QZaq8re4qSgz_qDKm8wxxvZNvprthvom/19" style="display: flex; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 12px; margin-left: 12px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="80"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/it8T3o57W274/v8/-1x-1.png" alt="Zero" width="80"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="零" height="80" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/it8T3o57W274/v8/-1x-1.png" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 8px; display: block;" width="80" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 12px; margin-left: 12px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;零&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 4